oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Sarah Fields Woods
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Sarah Fields Woods (1840-1910) seated in rocking chair in a dress.

Sarah Fields Woods was born in North Carolina in 1840 and died on March 23, 1910. She was the wife of Redmon (Redman) Woods whom she married in February 1885. She is buried at (Belmont) Hayes Cemetery in Arlington, Tennessee. She was the great-great-great grandmother of the donor.
